===Noun===
'''gasogene'''
# A type of [[Victorian]] [[seltzer bottle|seltzer-bottle]], which consisted of two mesh-encased glass globes arranged so that a reaction between [[tartaric acid]] and [[sodium bicarbonate]] produced [[carbon dioxide]] gas which [[carbonated]] the enclosed [[beverage]] and expelled it through a [[siphon]] valve.

